==German==
===Preposition===

Two way prepostition taking either the accusative or dative case. Accusative implying motion, (e.g where to?), dative implying location, eg (where?).

'''Meanings'''
#[[on]] -- es liegt ''auf dem'' Tisch (it is on the table) dat
#[[onto]] -- stell es ''auf den'' Tisch (place it on the table) acc

===Interjection===
'''auf!'''
#[[Carry on]]!
#[[have a go]]!

